title: [Jirkirl's Hilltop, Arena Nexus]
description: The surrounding area holds a semi-circle of wooden benches, each adjacent to its own challenge arena.  Behind the benches, a small copse of ribbon-bedecked fir trees lends a festive atmosphere to the site, and offers a slight break from frigid breezes.
paths: Obvious paths: east, southeast, south, southwest, west
